{"tid":400697,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"回合制RPG《Battle Chasers: Nightwar》10月4號正式推出","createTime":"2017-09-15T04:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T04:36:38.000Z","uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"265fd49d5c4d006189c33285d3d0b59013415f2b","tid":400697,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T04:36:38.000Z","msg":"《Battle Chasers: Nightwar》是一款根據 1998 年由 Joe Madureira 所繪製的漫畫作品「Battle Chasers」所製作的 RPG 作品，而該款遊戲的開發團隊為前《末世騎士》開發成員所組成的 Airship Syndicate 工作室負責製作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.gbc.tw/gb_img/3447314l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gbc.tw%2Fgb_img%2F3447314l.jpg&h=8d88411b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/ReFVV79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FReFVV79&h=53290b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/gFR0W27\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FgFR0W27&h=957b91b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OZ4PHjcfcz0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOZ4PHjcfcz0&d=LudQIL6f%2B2Q6d8%2BvPPualQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=89124eef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OZ4PHjcfcz0</a><br />\n<br />\n《Battle Chasers: Nightwar》首次亮相為 2015 年，在募資平台 Kickstarter 上募得足夠的資金後便進入開發階段。而在經歷長久的等待後，開發團隊也終於在近期宣布《Battle Chasers: Nightwar》將在今年 10 月 4 號於 Steam 正式推出，而除了 PC 外，PS4 、Xbox One 以及 Nintendo Switch 版本也會同步上市，期待該作的玩家們可別錯過了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}